  Desperate Housewives actress Eva, 47, looked stunning in a black, floor length evening gown. The garment featured a tasteful cut-out at the front, which was held together by a thin piece of string. The star accessorised with a simple pair of pearl earrings. She finished off the look with a sleek, up-do and a smokey eye.  Venus, 41, and Serena, 40, also looked incredibly glam ahead of the event. Venus wore a short, red dress made of different tassels with a tied neck. Serena wore a high-necked, bodycon dress made of a shiny, metallic material. The sisters stunned in high-heeled stilettos and posed confidently for the camera.  